### RxDB: Insert a New Todo Document Locally

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs-src/docs/articles/local-first-future.md

Inserts a new todo document into the 'todos' collection using RxDB. This operation is performed locally and instantly, demonstrating the immediate responsiveness of a local-first architecture without network calls.

```typescript
await db.todos.insert({
  id: 'todo1',
  title: 'Learn RxDB local-first',
  done: false,
  timestamp: new Date().toISOString()
});
```

